{"tid":2131204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小心唔好畀人spin走轉移視線","createTime":"2020-07-29T16:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:14:50.000Z","uid":329733,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5dab08c35f38672e689f6818eea637958ea3db","tid":2131204,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"呢幾日港共班仆街放風話要押後選舉<br />\n點知國際線上個個都話要留意選舉<br />\n就連十一哥條撚樣都話押後選舉好危險<br />\n呢個消息一出畀人屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢頭就無啦啦執行國安法拉鳩班 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">前</span></span> 學生動源嘅𡃁仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然黑警砌生豬肉、濫捕同惡法係要mon實<br />\n但亦都唔排除港共會暗渡陳倉, 分散大衆對押後選舉的注意, 將大家對押後選舉嘅情緒spin去黨安法<br />\n<br />\n應承我, 係打輿論戰救手足時, 唔好唔記得對家想永續萬年立會,剝奪選舉權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f60e0b4516f3d2f82c3e74bc84c2b61eaa1835","tid":2131204,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"46f144831ada1830adb25f7378166a77e7218e9c","tid":2131204,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"6e0cc3056685906d316d6cbb5456d9e181cfe9f7","tid":2131204,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:33:20.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c7a57d034c8e042dee850b195110c6a2a0aee8","tid":2131204,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-2